      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Clara Agent Automation Pipeline\n\n**Before running:**\n1. Start the API server:\n   `py -3.10 scripts/api_server.py`\n2. Click **Execute Workflow** below\n\nFull 5-step pipeline:\n1. Transcribe onboarding audio/video (Whisper)\n2. Extract account data from demo transcripts\n3. Generate v1 agent specs\n4. Apply onboarding updates (v2 memo)\n5. Generate v2 agent specs",
